Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶油蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有什么能做好的秘诀 能教教我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 最重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 这是我家的配方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35}巧克力奶油蛋糕的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30}材料
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,低筋面粉 120g
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,可可粉   12g
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,泡打粉   一小勺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,砂糖     100g
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,无盐黄油  100g
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,鸡蛋     中号大小的2个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力   适量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,牛奶     适量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30}工具
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕模具 量勺 筛子\N面盆 打泡器 橡胶铲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍稍调整了一下配方 在家也能做出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先照这个做做看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢店长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:01:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道能不能做好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题 做点心就像做数学一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要正确掌握材料份量 按照规定步骤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会得到相同的结果 相同的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就是爱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心里一边想着吃蛋糕的人一边做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵要烤蛋糕？好厉害啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想明天爬山的时候带去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不出小葵还喜欢户外呢 好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟男朋友去？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有女生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵这么可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上当心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会买手礼回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？谢谢小葵 小光好高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心里想着吃蛋糕的人高兴的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确 就算吃蛋糕的人是日向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着一脸满足的表情来吃的话…心里还是有点高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！加油做出充满爱情的蛋糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管有不少插曲 明天终于要和日向履约去爬谷川岳了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有小枫学姐和可可娜酱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:30.27,title,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜的饭能大冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:35.36,note,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜：
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:35.36,note,NTP,0,0,0,,提前一天祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:35.36,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}Happy Birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:35.36,note,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚一起庆祝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:35.36,note,NTP,100,0,0,,by 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨衣和替换的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水和零食
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 再拿一条毛巾去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…生日礼物？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还不能打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要…打开了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前说过想要登山靴来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈还记着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尺码正好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去…吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去爬天览山吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然…对了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那里看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也让你收下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好凉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好几年没来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:37.11,yama_neta,NTP,0,0,0,,饭能市曙光儿童森林公园 位于饭能市政府附近 因高度再现了芬兰卡通姆明（Moomins）的世界而著名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的仿佛置身于故事的世界一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦马
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦马
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦～马～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里 或许还真的有精灵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道真会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈好晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦马
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 回来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:10:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天去谷川岳吧 所以想今天给你庆生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点心店都关门了 只好买便利店的蛋糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 生日礼物已经准备好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天收拾行李的时候不小心看到了 给我打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈没藏好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好高兴 谢谢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尺寸刚刚好 一高兴就走着去儿童森林公园了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走到那么远？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 稍微有点热 风很舒服 景色也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还读了小时候的书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,树叶在夕阳下闪闪发光好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈也是为了给我赶上而买来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真的是好快乐的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 可可娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快乐 可可娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那咱们吃蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充满爱情的蛋糕终于好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 都这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶紧睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们再一起来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好了 绝对哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…但是 诺言实现之后又会如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登上谷川岳 下山 然后呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦马
